flowchart TB
  classDef boundary fill:#111827,stroke:#6b7280,color:#f3f4f6;
  classDef k8s fill:#0f3d4c,stroke:#14b8a6,color:#e6fffa;
  classDef ext fill:#1f2937,stroke:#a78bfa,color:#ede9fe;
  classDef data fill:#1e293b,stroke:#f59e0b,color:#ffedd5;

  subgraph Internet
    Browser[Institution + Operator Browsers]:::boundary
    ApiClient[Enterprise API Clients]:::boundary
  end

  Ingress[ALB / API Gateway Ingress]:::boundary
  Browser --> Ingress
  ApiClient --> Ingress

  subgraph EKS Cluster
    direction TB
    APIGW[Platform API Gateway]:::k8s
    Ctrl[Control Plane Services<br/>identity, policy, tenant, integration mgr]:::k8s
    DataPlane[Data Plane Services<br/>workflow, document, review, audit, notifications]:::k8s
    Conn[Connector Gateway]:::k8s
    Workers[Async Workers]:::k8s
    APIGW --> Ctrl
    APIGW --> DataPlane
    DataPlane --> Conn
    DataPlane --> Workers
  end

  Ingress --> APIGW

  subgraph Capability Services
    OCR[esheria-ocr on SageMaker Endpoint]:::ext
    Contract[esheria-contract-engine API]:::ext
    Research[esheria-ai retrieval API]:::ext
    Drafting[lexdraft API]:::ext
    InternalAnalytics[esheria-analytics API]:::ext
  end

  Conn --> OCR
  Conn --> Contract
  Conn --> Research
  Conn --> Drafting
  Conn --> InternalAnalytics

  subgraph Data and Infra
    TxDB[(Transactional DB)]:::data
    Obj[(Object Storage)]:::data
    Queue[(Event Bus / Queue)]:::data
    Search[(Search / Retrieval Index)]:::data
    Metrics[(Analytics Warehouse)]:::data
    Obs[(Logs / Traces / Metrics)]:::data
    Secrets[(Secrets + Config)]:::data
  end

  DataPlane --> TxDB
  DataPlane --> Obj
  DataPlane --> Queue
  DataPlane --> Search
  DataPlane --> Metrics
  Ctrl --> Secrets
  APIGW --> Obs
  DataPlane --> Obs
  Conn --> Obs

